snippet.title: TIME SOUL Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
TIME SOUL is a souls-like action-platformer with a generative worlds and platforms. 

Steam: store.steampowered.com/app/2928270/TIME_SOUL

Defeat‎‎‎ time guardians, collect clocks and shards, and stop time before facing the Timelord. Randomized bosses, mobs, 300+items, 50+weapons and spells, Conquer the galaxy in 60 minutes!
